r: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bor=
der-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #c=
cc;">  which is up</a> since FTX invested, which is more than you can say f=
or FTT.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The complaint says that FT=
X paid for much of Kives=E2=80=99s=C2=A0and Baum's stakes in K5 with =E2=80=
=9C$250 million in shares of FTX Trading Ltd. and West Realm Shires, Inc.,=
=E2=80=9D which I=E2=80=99m pretty sure are worth zero now. So arguably it =
did get equivalent value for=C2=A0<em>that</em>. Magic beans for magic bean=
s.</li>
