319a23cBd165feab" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"=
_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-b=
ottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid;=
 background-color: #ccc;">  the SEC sued Bittrex Inc.</a>, a crypto exchang=
e, for operating an unregistered securities exchange. Bittrex responded by,=
 among other things, shutting down its US business and <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31906837.263401/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb2=
