<div id=3D"footnote-4" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[4] This does not work in reverse: If the shar=
es trade at $100, there is no corresponding mechanism to capture the differ=
ence between the $100 million market cap and the $55 million real value. Th=
is is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31906837.263=
